## OnChainIndex v1.0.0

Initial public release of OnChainIndex — an independent index ranking on-chain applications by real usage.

### What’s included
- Usage-based rankings (Most Active, Most Used, Trending)
- Daily ranking snapshots with preserved history
- Public, read-only API
- dApp profile pages with plain-English descriptions
- “Verified by GwapScore” credibility indicator
- Embeddable ranking widgets with attribution
- Public, versioned methodology

### What this release is not
- Rankings are not endorsements
- Rankings are not safety or investment advice
- No paid placement or promotional influence

### Stability
This release prioritizes determinism, transparency, and reproducibility.
Methodology changes are versioned and documented.

### Looking ahead
Future releases will focus on alerts, historical analysis, and ecosystem integrations without altering v1 ranking guarantees.